# AddFMA — Personal Preferences

Copy this file to:
  ~/.claude/Skills/PAI/USER/SKILLCUSTOMIZATIONS/AddFMA/PREFERENCES.md

Then fill in your values. The skill reads this file before executing any workflow.

## Required Variables

- `FLEET_REPO` = `/path/to/your/fleet/fleet`
- `GITHUB_USER` = `your-github-username`

## Worktree Pattern

- Worktrees: `{FLEET_REPO}/.worktrees/{APP_SLUG}`
- Branch pattern: `{GITHUB_USER}-add-fma-{APP_SLUG}`
- Assignee: `{GITHUB_USER}`
